<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>12635</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17694</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第二天早上，警察把杰佩托送回家。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17695</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20906</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这时，匹诺曹正在家里哭。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20907</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25217</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他又累又饿，还没有衣服穿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25218</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>30699</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当杰佩托回到家时，他很生气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>30700</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>34399</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你是个坏孩子，匹诺曹。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>34400</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39050</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你必须尊重我，听我的话。”杰佩托说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39051</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>45246</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的，爸爸。对不起。”匹诺曹说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>45247</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>49007</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那天早上，他决定尝试做个好孩子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>49008</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52079</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>做坏孩子并没有什么意思。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52080</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57093</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他知道，如果他向杰佩托道歉，他就会得到食物。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57094</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>67717</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我昨晚真的很想你，爸爸。”匹诺曹说。不过这次是真的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>67718</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72982</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他希望杰佩托可以一直在这里给他食物，让他开心。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72983</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>79066</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>相反，他昨天又冷又饿，蟋蟀先生还把他弄哭了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>79067</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86264</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰佩托听到自己的儿子说想念他，心里非常高兴。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86265</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89124</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他并不想生匹诺曹的气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89125</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>92170</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “可怜的孩子。”他说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>92171</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99200</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你看起来很累。你一定又饿又冷。我们吃早餐吧。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99201</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103665</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，我给你做衣服穿。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103666</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>107719</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰佩托从口袋里面拿出三个梨。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>107720</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>110215</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他是在回家的路上摘的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>110216</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>114089</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>不过，在他还没来得及细细品尝时，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>114090</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117749</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>匹诺曹已经把三个梨都吃掉了！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117750</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>123640</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦！我还是很饿！”匹诺曹抱怨道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>123641</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>131292</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好吧，你不应该浪费食物。把核也啃干净。”杰佩托说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>131293</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134389</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>匹诺曹吃掉了核。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134390</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>137286</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你说得对，爸爸。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>137287</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142330</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我觉得饱多了。你早餐吃了什么？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142331</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145488</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你的微笑。”杰佩托回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145489</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>151798</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>匹诺曹这才意识到他把杰佩托的早餐都吃掉了！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>151799</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>160756</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，爸爸！对不起，我吃了你的早餐，而我居然不知道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>160757</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>166206</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我真的很自私。我会为你做任何事情。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>166207</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>171512</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>如果你想要我去上学，我也可以。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>171513</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>174184</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“真的吗？”杰佩托问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>174185</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>179469</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>儿子终于开始转变了，杰佩托感到很欣慰。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>179470</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>184004</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的，但首先我需要买教科书。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>184005</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>188265</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我可以要一些钱吗？”匹诺曹问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>188266</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>193713</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，我没有什么钱。”杰佩托伤心地说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>193714</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>197816</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “不过别担心。我一定会帮你拿到书的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>197817</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>202491</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他穿上外套，离开了家。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>202492</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>208585</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他很快就回来了。杰佩托给了匹诺曹他的第一本书。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>208586</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>214675</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>匹诺曹从杰佩托那里接过书，发现杰佩托的外套不见了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>214676</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>222332</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谢谢。但是爸爸，你的外套去哪里了？”匹诺曹问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>222333</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>228002</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，我不需要外套。这几天太热了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>228003</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>230721</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰佩托低着头回答道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>230722</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>235815</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰佩托为了给匹诺曹买书，卖掉了自己的大衣！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>235816</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>240245</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>匹诺曹流下了幸福的泪水。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>240246</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>243602</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谢谢你，爸爸！”他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>243603</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>247310</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他给了杰佩托一个大大的拥抱。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>247311</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>252098</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在，我们开始做衣服吧。”杰佩托说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>252099</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>256136</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这一天，他们一直在给匹诺曹做衣服。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>256137</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>263883</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>明天就是匹诺曹上学的第一天了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>